description: Erection of a mixed-use development of six buildings between twelve and twenty storeys (plus two basement levels) comprising 752 residential units, including affordable housing, a hotel, flexible commercial uses at ground and first floor levels including retail, restaurant, bar, caf, offices, gallery and crche uses (A1, A2, A3, A4, & D1), associated car and bicycle parking, and landscaping including provision of riverside walk.
